question: From the step response, estimate (a) percent overshoot (%) and (b) 2% settling time (s). Show your reasoning steps.
gold_chain_json: ["Identify the steady-state value from the final plateau of the response.", "Identify the peak value (maximum amplitude) from the curve.", "Compute percent overshoot = (peak − steady_state) / steady_state × 100%.", "Compute 2% settling time as the first time after which the response stays within ±2% of steady-state."]
